  "text": "It should be noted, however, that such statistical analyses can detect only correlations but not causal relationships. To establish which of these factors certainly affects soldier production in C. arma, future experimental studies are needed. In T. styraci, development of an artificial diet rearing system has enabled exquisite experimental approaches to the mechanisms underlying soldier differentiation and control [CITATION_1] [CITATION_2] [CITATION_3] . Development of similar experimental system for C. arma is desirable.",
